title: American Daydreams - Naomi Woods [720p]
description:
JMac is hanging out with his friend's sister, Naomi Woods, when the pizza guy arrives. Naomi is bored talking to JMac and decides she would have more fun with the pizza guy. JMac can't believe how incredibly lucky the pizza guy is to have Naomi want him, so JMac nods off and starts day dreaming of being the pizza guy and having Naomi want his big sausage.
